Folder Descriptions :
---------------------

* c1222/stack :  Contains all files required to run a c1222 client integrated with the policy engine and a c1222 server

* x86_detector : Contains all the source files of the x86 detector


Compilation Instructions :
--------------------------

System Requirements :
---------------------

	Windows XP or higher, borland compiler


Compiling the Client :
---------------------

>> cd x86_detection/src/c1222/stack/client
>> make
>> cd OUT
>> make


Compiling the Server :
----------------------

>> cd x86_detection/src/c1222/stack/server
>> make
>> cd OUT
>> make

Starting the Server :
---------------------

>> cd x86_detection/src/c1222/stack/server/OUT/Bin/
>> ./c1222test_server.exe


Starting the x86 detector : (Start the x86 detetor before the Client)
---------------------------------------------------------------------

>> cd x86_detection/src/x86_detector
>> python x86_detection_experiment <path_to_classifier>

e.g:

>> python x86_detector x86_detection_experiment x86_detection/classifier


Starting the Client :
---------------------

>> cd x86_detection/src/c1222/stack/client/OUT/Bin/
>> ./c1222test_client.exe

